    <item>
      <title>英国出生父母的生育率跌至历史最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/uk-births-to-british-born-parents-tumble-to-lowest-on-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于生活成本上升和生活方式的改变削弱了英国人生育孩子的愿望，去年英国父母均出生在本国的婴儿比例自有记录以来首次下滑至 60% 以下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/uk-births-to-british-born-parents-tumble-to-lowest-on-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 16:20:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
